{
  "title": "U lusay nu sepatay a palaedan",
  "titleCh": "四季產物",
  "soundPath": null,
  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "在四季中有各種不同的果樹。春季是梅雨季節，每天都下著雨，樹木長得非常茂盛，也長出雨來菇、箭荀、桂竹荀、攀爬的菜類，如絲瓜、苦瓜、豆類…",
      "ab": "Adihay ku kasarumaruma nu lusay tina sepat nu palaedan. U kaveneran a palaedan i kacanglahan, u kaurauradan tu a remiamiad, kapah ku maluvic nu kilang, adihay ku langaw, u lalupela, adeci, u tevu’ nu tukus, u milaladay a dateng i, u runi, u kakurut, u lumingay.",
